criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  HIV infected;

          -  ≥18 years of age;

          -  speak and read either Estonian or Russian;

          -  receiving or starting a HAART regimen

        Exclusion Criteria:

        - triple class antiretroviral drug resistance, as determined from a prior resistance test
        performed in clinical practice, defined according to International Antiviral Society - USA
        (IAS-USA) interpretive guidelines for genotypic resistance mutations
